{"tid":1324521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"各位巴絲，你地相信一切係「整定」定係「事在人為」？","createTime":"2019-07-16T14:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T10:40:07.000Z","uid":90522,"like":69,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c8a48b40acd98ba9c6a325776f408f7d9766391c","tid":1324521,"uid":90522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"整定=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事在人為=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信一切係<span style=\"color: red;\">整定</span>為前提既，不過可以透過人為去補救，<br />\n但大局而定。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，<br />\n如果一個人先天有Cancer基因<br />\n咁佢生Cancer就係「整定」既<br />\n但佢可以透過後天去補救<br />\n例如做多D運動，食多D菜，<br />\n去降低Cancer對佢身體既傷害。<br />\n<br />\n講咁多<br />\n其實我係相信一切都係整定既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fc4b49fc9cc6fc43065b5802e53f6c02c1c83c","tid":1324521,"uid":281268,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"Half half<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac472e125c5640c7549ca52eb08a7fc9d97d4d8","tid":1324521,"uid":522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:00:32.000Z","msg":"整定係框架，而事在人為係框架之內令到件事做到最好"},{"pid":"8adac717742f08e5150b19a73af075a0921ae9ca","tid":1324521,"uid":90522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"如果 一切就是最好的安排<br />\n你當年難道有錯麼？"},{"pid":"b69c56d005bf7019f377759a0a7d430db3c56065","tid":1324521,"uid":90522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92fc4b49fc9cc6fc43065b5802e53f6c02c1c83c","tid":1324521,"uid":281268,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"Half half<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"咁你偏向相信邊一邊?"},{"pid":"4542b17f49388ff087428d33790748d6b50527c3","tid":1324521,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":